@park23: the function definition of onGetProfilePicture of your code is incorrect.
You can use the following (picture file name can be something else) - 

```php
function onGetProfilePicture($from, $target, $type, $data) {
    $pictureof = explode("@", $target);
    $pictureof = $pictureof[0];
    $time = time();
    $filename = $pictureof . "_@_" . $time . ".jpg";
    $filename = WhatsProt::PICTURES_FOLDER."/" . $filename;
    $fp = @fopen($filename, "w");
    if ($fp) {
        fwrite($fp, $data);
        fclose($fp);
    }
}
```

